{
  "version": "2.1",
  "description": "gendoc 文件流水線定義 — 此檔案是流水線的唯一順序來源。新增文件類型：(1) 加入本檔案的 steps；(2) 建立 templates/{TYPE}.md + TYPE.gen.md + TYPE.review.md。不需修改任何 skill 檔案。",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "D01-IDEA",
      "type": "IDEA",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/IDEA.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-auto",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D01-IDEA]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D02-BRD",
      "type": "BRD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/BRD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-auto",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D02-BRD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D03-PRD",
      "type": "PRD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/PRD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D03-PRD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D03.5-CONSTANTS",
      "type": "CONSTANTS",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/CONSTANTS.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D03.5-CONSTANTS]",
      "note": "從 PRD 提取所有關鍵業務數值（倍率、閾值、SLO、RTP、rate-limit 等）到 docs/CONSTANTS.md（並同步輸出 docs/constants.json）。下游所有文件（EDD/BDD/test-plan/runbook）生成時必須讀取此文件並引用，確保跨文件數值一致性。這是 AI 可實作性的核心機制。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D04-PDD",
      "type": "PDD",
      "layer": "需求層",
      "output": ["docs/PDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D04-PDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D05-VDD",
      "type": "VDD",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/VDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D05-VDD]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D06-EDD",
      "type": "EDD",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/EDD.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D06-EDD]",
      "note": "EDD 生成採用三 subagent 多 pass 架構（見 EDD.gen.md）：Pass-A 生成 §1-§8，Pass-B 生成 §4.5 UML，Pass-C 生成 §9-§21。三個 pass 均輸出到同一個 docs/EDD.md，review loop 在全部完成後執行。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D07-ARCH",
      "type": "ARCH",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ARCH.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D07-ARCH]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D07b-UML",
      "type": "UML",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/diagrams/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/diagrams/*.md",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-diagrams",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D07b-UML]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-diagrams skill，生成 9 大 UML 圖 + class-inventory.md。不走標準 gen→review 流程。class-inventory.md 供 D11-test-plan 和 D13-RTM 讀取。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D08-API",
      "type": "API",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/API.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D08-API]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D09-SCHEMA",
      "type": "SCHEMA",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/SCHEMA.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D09-SCHEMA]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D10-FRONTEND",
      "type": "FRONTEND",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/FRONTEND.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D10-FRONTEND]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D10b-AUDIO",
      "type": "AUDIO",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/AUDIO.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type == game",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D10b-AUDIO]",
      "note": "音效設計文件：BGM/SFX/VO 清單、音效觸發邏輯、引擎設定（Cocos/Unity/HTML5 Web Audio）、資產規格、效能預算"
    },
    {
      "id": "D10c-ANIM",
      "type": "ANIM",
      "layer": "設計層",
      "output": ["docs/ANIM.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "client_type == game",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D10c-ANIM]",
      "note": "動畫特效設計文件：骨骼動畫/幀動畫/Tween/粒子/Shader、引擎設定（Cocos/Unity/HTML5 PixiJS）、效能預算與 LOD 策略"
    },
    {
      "id": "D11-test-plan",
      "type": "test-plan",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["docs/test-plan.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D11-test-plan]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D12-BDD-server",
      "type": "BDD-server",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["features/"],
      "output_glob": "features/*.feature",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "test(gendoc)[D12-BDD-server]",
      "note": "BDD-server.gen.md 指示生成多個 .feature 檔案 + step definitions skeleton；BDD-server.review.md 審查所有 features/*.feature（含上游 PRD/CONSTANTS 數值對照）"
    },
    {
      "id": "D12b-BDD-client",
      "type": "BDD-client",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["features/client/"],
      "output_glob": "features/client/*.feature",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != none",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "test(gendoc)[D12b-BDD-client]",
      "note": "BDD-client.gen.md 指示生成多個 .feature 檔案 + step definitions skeleton；BDD-client.review.md 審查所有 features/client/*.feature（含上游 PRD/CONSTANTS 數值對照）"
    },
    {
      "id": "D13-RTM",
      "type": "RTM",
      "layer": "品質層",
      "output": ["docs/RTM.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D13-RTM]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D14-runbook",
      "type": "runbook",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/runbook.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D14-runbook]"
    },
    {
      "id": "D15-LOCAL_DEPLOY",
      "type": "LOCAL_DEPLOY",
      "layer": "運維層",
      "output": ["docs/LOCAL_DEPLOY.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D15-LOCAL_DEPLOY]",
      "note": "LOCAL_DEPLOY.gen.md 要求生成後自動執行 docker/sandbox 驗證，確認所有命令可成功執行"
    },
    {
      "id": "D16-ALIGN",
      "type": "ALIGN",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-check",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D16-ALIGN]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-align-check skill，不走標準 gen→review 流程"
    },
    {
      "id": "D16-ALIGN-F",
      "type": "ALIGN-F",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-fix",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D16-ALIGN-F]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：依 ALIGN_REPORT.md 自動修復對齊問題（all layers），每條 fix verify 後 commit。緊接 D16-ALIGN 執行。完成後必須觸發 D16b-ALIGN-VERIFY 重新驗證。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D16b-ALIGN-VERIFY",
      "type": "ALIGN-VERIFY",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/ALIGN_REPORT.md"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-align-check",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D16b-ALIGN-VERIFY]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：D16-ALIGN-F 修復完成後重新執行 gendoc-align-check，更新 ALIGN_REPORT.md 為修復後狀態，確認修復效果。若仍有 CRITICAL/HIGH 問題，繼續修復直到清零。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D17-CONTRACTS",
      "type": "CONTRACTS",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/blueprint/contracts/", "docs/blueprint/infra/", "docs/blueprint/scaffold/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/blueprint/contracts/**/*",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-contracts",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[D17-CONTRACTS]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：從生成文件提取機器可讀規格（OpenAPI YAML, JSON Schema, Pact, IaC, Seed Code）。輸出集中於 docs/blueprint/ 目錄。生成後自動執行 openapi-spec-validator 驗證及 path 數量對齊檢查。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D18-MOCK",
      "type": "MOCK",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/blueprint/mock/"],
      "output_glob": "docs/blueprint/mock/**/*",
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != api-only",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-mock",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[D18-MOCK]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-mock skill，生成 FastAPI mock server + 擬真假資料 + frontend 使用手冊。生成後自動執行 python main.py --check 確認可啟動。整個 docs/blueprint/mock/ 目錄可獨立帶走使用。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D20-PROTOTYPE",
      "type": "PROTOTYPE",
      "layer": "實作層",
      "output": ["docs/pages/prototype/"],
      "multi_file": true,
      "condition": "client_type != api-only",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-prototype",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "feat(gendoc)[D20-PROTOTYPE]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-prototype skill，依 PDD/FRONTEND/API.md 生成可點擊的 HTML prototype（UI 流程展示）+ API explorer（交互式 API 文件）。輸出至 docs/pages/prototype/，由 D19-HTML 的 gen_html.py 自動連結到 sidebar。"
    },
    {
      "id": "D19-HTML",
      "type": "HTML",
      "layer": "稽核層",
      "output": ["docs/pages/"],
      "multi_file": false,
      "condition": "always",
      "special_skill": "gendoc-gen-html",
      "handled_by": "gendoc-flow",
      "commit_prefix": "docs(gendoc)[D19-HTML]",
      "note": "特殊步驟：呼叫 gendoc-gen-html skill，不走標準 gen→review 流程。Step 1-B 開頭偵測並刪除舊版 generate_site.py（若存在），強制使用 gen_html.py。"
    }
  ]
}
